            . I am brother to Samuel Everingham, a <rs id="t18260622-142-viclabel708" type="occupation">hosier</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18260622-142-victim838 t18260622-142-viclabel708"></join>. On the 5th of June, about half-past one o'clock in the day, my attention was called by a person calling Thief! I went and saw the prisoner going from our door, and turning down <placeName id="t18260622-142-crimeloc709">Berwick-street</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18260622-142-crimeloc709" type="placeName" value="Berwick-street"></interp>
