                     <interp inst="t18260622-142-person840" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I was standing in Noel-street about half-past one o'clock, and saw the prisoner run out of Berwick-street into Noel-street; he threw this parcel down by me, and I took it up and held it till Mr. Bertraun came up, and then I went to Marlborough-street.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I picked them up at the corner of Berwick-street.</p>
